div.div: Senpai ga Uzai Kouhai no Hanashi

Being seen as a full-fledged business woman isn’t easy for Futaba Igarashi when her senpai, Harumi, treats her like a kid. Days for her are never typical, at work or outside of it, with all the antics going on in her life. As mishaps ensue, she’ll find herself growing closer with her loudmouth senpai. Maybe Futaba feels more than she lets on, but one thing’s for sure: she’s still annoyed!
(Source: Funimation)

The protagonist, Naoya, is a first-year in high school. He asks out Saki, a girl he has been in love with, and she agrees to be his girlfriend. He's currently on cloud nine. But then, a beautiful girl named Nagisa comes up to Naoya one day and tells him that she wants to go out with him. Naoya feels himself wavering because Nagisa is such a good girl, and he comes to a decision! A new kind of romcom from a rather unexpected decision is about to begin!
(Source: Crunchyroll)
Inma Tsuihou: Hentai Gift wo Sazukatta Sei de Outo Owareru mo, Onnanoko to "Nakayoku" suru Dake de Chouzetsu Level Up

A world where one's life is decided by one's talent, called a "Gift." The main character, Erio Scarlet, who was born in the house of an influential noble family that had produced a lot of Holy Knights, manifested a suspicious Gift called "Incubus" in the conferment ceremony. Furthermore, the only skill attached to that Gift was one embarrassingly called "Peerless."
Erio was banished from the city because there was no way his indecent existence could be permitted in a family of Holy Knights, but... somehow he went through an amazing growth when he dealt with his horniness?! In addition, when his childhood friend who was bestowed with the Gift "Sacred Knight" chased after him and reverse ra... did it with him, a lot of powerful indecent skills showed up, and on top of that they even got bound by Master-Servant contract...?!
This is the indecent heroic tale of the boy who was gifted with and indecent Gift rising in the world while "getting along" with a lot of girls.
Matching App de Moto Koibito to Saikai Shita.

Sho Fujigaya is a university student who has long since broken up with his girlfriend. On a matchmaking app he started on the recommendation of a friend, he found someone he could have a good conversation with. What's more, the app shows that their compatibility is 98%! A good opportunity to start a new relationship. But on the agreed date, the person who is at the meeting place is Hikaru Takamiya, his ex-girlfriend! They argue as they did back then, but regret and dissatisfaction seep into their hearts...
